      Description & Documents

      Recharge in. your private haven in. our ANZZI ONE pc man-made stone freestanding soaking bathtub in. transcendent regal blue. Crafted with Precision out of man-made stone in. a mind and body invigorating regal blue color with a transparent Finish and accented by a pop-push drain in. polish chrome. Not only will our Ember add a pop of color, it will Enhance your personal serenity with its ergonomic design which makes it perfect for an end-of-day D soak. Paired with the luxurious ANZZI Kros Frees

      • Free standing soaking bathtub
      • Includes ANZZI Kros freestanding faucet FS-AZ0025CH
      • 1-piece man-made stone in transcendent regal blue
      • Center drain
      • ONE (1) Person Capacity
      • Dimensions 66 in L x 32.5 in W x 23.5 in H
      • Tub Weight 308 lbs.
      • Pop-push drain and easy and straight forward installation
      • Ships from factory within 24 hours of order
      • To speak to a knowledgeable and dedicated ANZZI specialist simply call 1-844-44-ANZZI or visit us on the WEB at www.ANZZI.com
      • Lifetime Warranty
